TY  - JOUR
T1  - The Capacitated Lot-Sizing Problem with Linked Lot Sizes
AU  - Suerie, Christopher
AU  - Stadtler, Hartmut
Y1  - 2003/08/01
PY  - 2003
DA  - 2003/08/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.49.8.1039.16406
